{"tid":305542,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個快速KO痱滋嘅方法","createTime":"2017-07-01T17:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T01:04:34.000Z","uid":113207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"849a9a344d793f05fedc1c7906eba0e1755454f8","tid":305542,"uid":113207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"手足口病嘅小弟<br />\n依家個口至少有十粒痱滋<br />\n已經試過用鹽㩒住粒痱滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但都冇用 <br />\n各位巴絲打 有冇咩獨門秘方打救小弟"},{"pid":"e0a1af1f5c8ad59289bd0b2a6158d1f1b5d596a5","tid":305542,"uid":4679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"龜苓膏好似有用"},{"pid":"419b67fe71f4a9295a211cd9262a2b55ae681c3f","tid":305542,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:50:24.000Z","msg":"萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛"},{"pid":"a4ee81fb71bfc836944be68f221b0c859514c6a3","tid":305542,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n生一次, 要重新買一次?"},{"pid":"ff09311521f1cab502ecde40af832542c359a40f","tid":305542,"uid":70150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n呢支真係痛到仆街<br />\n有陣粒野大要點兩下真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次用都要鼓起好大勇氣諗好耐"},{"pid":"2051350c73c175cef9fb4f15ca9da66455b58eec","tid":305542,"uid":62809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"早排生咗粒痱滋 早午晚李斯德林 都要十日先至好"},{"pid":"c19e94eddc7e0b65a33f848d3e1b7baa70055b16","tid":305542,"uid":113207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n生一次, 要重新買一次?</blockquote><br />\n我依家十幾粒痱滋  一枝夠唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae84bf5f69bc52576bfcb135c76828280e72416","tid":305542,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n生一次, 要重新買一次?</blockquote><br />\n我依家十幾粒痱滋  一枝夠唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係果下痛完之後, 第2日都唔會再痛?"},{"pid":"9a1bc25ca07877a8618fcebbf1d611b741c5d16d","tid":305542,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:38:10.000Z","msg":"食奇異果<br />\n同埋一定一定要飲好多水<br />\n手足口病 有排你痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446738677765c7a4059f84faa7f875ac2cacd6b2","tid":305542,"uid":54258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"去家計會check真d係咪菲茲定其它野穩陣d"},{"pid":"d374ce5c1512fd47b1ede147afc90499acb285ed","tid":305542,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:12:37.000Z","msg":"都係用鹽水漱口 漱到啲白色野冇晒見到肉為止<br />\n然後過一陣 得閒又再漱<br />\n飲多啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得細個老豆幫我用雙氧水洗粒痱滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痛到仆街 但超快好返"},{"pid":"da241556177d2e567648b80f773643e2e14d91c7","tid":305542,"uid":115197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n生一次, 要重新買一次?</blockquote><br />\n我依家十幾粒痱滋  一枝夠唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係果下痛完之後, 第2日都唔會再痛?</blockquote><br />\n係 但係點落去果下真係爽過扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a584b34415de92dda926c706c43f3d8678b9ec1","tid":305542,"uid":115197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:14:04.000Z","msg":"Btw 早晚用漱口水可以預防飛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21701d26158a226539cf83d4ca0f96678bc43db8","tid":305542,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:20:36.000Z","msg":"萬靈有支噴霧或嗽口水同牌子<br />\n華潤堂有支叫口腔靈<br />\n極濃鹽水<br />\n一日幾個奇異果<br />\n一日飲勁多水<br />\n用牙籤篤穿佢"},{"pid":"8dfd88af36de9b0cb1175d883a1233e6788bf09f","tid":305542,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>萬寧有隻痱滋糕好有效<br />\n黃色面廿幾蚊支 整係用一次<br />\n一點落去痛到仆街 之後變咗白色<br />\n就feel唔到痛</blockquote><br />\n生一次, 要重新買一次?</blockquote><br />\n我依家十幾粒痱滋  一枝夠唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係果下痛完之後, 第2日都唔會再痛?</blockquote><br />\n佢話就話24個鐘唔痛,但我用左幾次都覺得有30-48個鐘"},{"pid":"288e51349e530372c6dae9e69ea57f711a53959d","tid":305542,"uid":68642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:27:55.000Z","msg":"認真 日本買個支小林 有用<br />\n我次次生親都手指甲咁大粒<br />\n用左佢初起個時查 會抑制到佢唔變大粒<br />\n同埋口服維他命b藥"},{"pid":"a6060ff93d64e67f8578b6cae511dafadd731c03","tid":305542,"uid":63515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:31:41.000Z","msg":"必妥碘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bafcd0d84526c8ebadf9f225bddda14c15c13d","tid":305542,"uid":112143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:38:20.000Z","msg":"苦瓜排骨湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d7c54df54e4e4be6e5e495f265e91310ecf61","tid":305542,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:44:07.000Z","msg":"整啲鹽上去最快好"},{"pid":"1404229a1d